snippet: An online campaign has raised nearly $300,000 for Cassidy Stay, the teenage survivor of a shooting attack in suburban Houston last week in which her parents and four siblings were killed....

headline.print_headline: Online Campaign Raises Nearly $300,000 for Texas Shooting Survivor
headline.main: Online Campaign Raises Nearly $300,000 for Texas Shooting Survivor

lead_paragraph: An online campaign has raised nearly $300,000 for Cassidy Stay, the teenage survivor of a shooting attack in suburban Houston last week in which her parents and four siblings were killed.
